title: A Hall of Fame Ring for Martina Hingis (International Tennis Hall of Fame)
text: ( Source : International Tennis Hall of Fame ) Swiss tennis great Martina Hingis , who is both a Hall of Famer and part of the current world No. 1 doubles team, was honored on center court at the BNP PARIBAS WTA Finals Singapore presented by SC
